function Window_Proxy(_original_window) {
  Object.defineProperty(this, 'XMLHttpRequest', { get: function() { return XMLHttpRequest_Proxy; } });
  var localStorage_proxy = new LocalStorage_Proxy(localStorage, localStorageCache);
  Object.defineProperty(this, 'localStorage', { get: function() { return localStorage_proxy; } });
  this._callbackCounter = 0;
  this.onload = null;
  Object.defineProperty(this, 'confirm', { get: function() { return function confirm_proxy(a,b,c,d,e) {
    return _original_window.confirm(a,b,c,d,e);
  } } });
  Object.defineProperty(this, 'alert', { get: function() { return function alert_proxy(a,b,c,d,e) {
    return _original_window.alert(a,b,c,d,e);
  } } });

  Object.defineProperty(this, 'window', { get: function() { return _this; } });
}

function XMLHttpRequest_Proxy() {
  this.open = function open(method, url) {
    if (url.charAt(0)!=='/') {
      var lastMachineSlash = machineXML.lastIndexOf('/');
      this._original_url = url;
      url = machineXML.slice(0,lastMachineSlash+1) + url;
    }

    this._url = url;
  };
  this.send = function send() {
    var _this = this;

    if (this.responseText = contentsByPath[this._url]) {
      this.status = 200;
      this.readyState = 4;
      this.responseText = contentsByPath[this._url];
      if (typeof this.responseText != 'string')
        this.responseText = JSON.stringify(this.responseText);
      setTimeout(function() { _this.onreadystatechange(); }, 1);
      return;
    }

      var xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();
      xhr.open('GET', 'http://www.pcjs.org'+this._url);
      xhr.onreadystatechange = function() {
        if (xhr.readyState!==4) return;
        if (xhr.status!==200) {
          _this.send_jsonp({data: { content: btoa(xhr.responseText) } });
          return;
        }
        _this.processResult(result);
      };
      xhr.send();
    }
    catch (xhrError) {
      this.send_jsonp();
    }
  };
  this.send_jsonp = function send_jsonp() {
    var _this = this;
    var callbackName = 'jsonpCallback'+(_window_proxy._callbackCounter++);
    window[callbackName] = function(result) {
      document.body.removeChild(reqScript);
      _this.processResult(result);
    };
    var reqScript = document.createElement('script');
    reqScript.src = embedPCURL+this._url+'?callback='+callbackName;
    document.body.appendChild(reqScript);
  };
  this.processResult = function(result) {
    if (!result.data.content) {
      alert(result.data.message +'\n'+this._url+'\n\n'+ JSON.stringify(result));
      return;
    }
    this.responseText = atob(result.data.content);
    contentsByPath[this._url] = this.responseText;
    if (this.responseText.charAt(0)!=='<') {
      try {
        contentsByPath[this._url] = JSON.parse(this.responseText);
      }
      catch (error) { }
    }
    var contentsByPathScript = document.getElementById('contentsByPathScript');
    if (!contentsByPathScript) {
      contentsByPathScript = document.createElement('script');
      contentsByPathScript.id = 'contentsByPathScript';
      document.body.appendChild(contentsByPathScript);

    this.readyState = 4;
    this.onreadystatechange();
  };
  this.setRequestHeader = function() { };
}

function LocalStorage_Proxy(_originalLocalStorage, _localStorageCache) {

  var updateDOMTimer = 0;
  var keys = [];
  this.length = 0;
  
  updateKeys();

  this.getItem = function getItem_proxy(key) {
    console.log('getItem_proxy('+JSON.stringify(key)+')');
    var cacheKey = key.indexOf(machineKey)===0 ? '{{*}}'+key.slice(machineKey.length) : key;
    return _localStorageCache[cacheKey] || _originalLocalStorage.getItem(key);
  };

  this.setItem = function setItem_proxy(key, value) {
    console.log('setItem_proxy('+JSON.stringify(key)+', '+JSON.stringify(value)+')');
    var cacheKey = key.indexOf(machineKey)===0 ? '{{*}}'+key.slice(machineKey.length) : key;
    _localStorageCache[cacheKey] = value;
    _originalLocalStorage.setItem(key, value);
  	updateKeys();
    clearTimeout(updateDOMTimer);
    updateDOMTimer = setTimeout(updateDOM, 100);
  };

  this.removeItem = function removeItem_proxy(key) {
    console.log('removeItem_proxy('+JSON.stringify(key)+')');
    var cacheKey = key.indexOf(machineKey)===0 ? '{{*}}'+key.slice(machineKey.length) : key;
    delete _localStorageCache[cacheKey];
    _originalLocalStorage.removeItem(key);
    updateKeys();
    clearTimeout(updateDOMTimer);
    updateDOMTimer = setTimeout(updateDOM, 100);
  };

  this.key = function key_proxy(index) {
    return keys[index];
  };

  function updateKeys() {
    for (var i = 0; i < _originalLocalStorage.length; i++) {
      keys.push(_originalLocalStorage.key(i));
    }
    for (var k in _localStorageCache) if (_localStorageCache.hasOwnProperty(k)) {
      var key = k.indexOf('{{*}}')===0 ? machineKey+k.slice('{{*}}'.length) : key;
      if (keys.indexOf(key)<0)
        keys.push(key);
    }
    this.length = keys.length;
  }

  function updateDOM() {
    var localStorageScript = document.getElementById('localStorageScript');
    if (!localStorageScript) {
      localStorageScript = document.createElement('script');
      localStorageScript.id = 'localStorageScript';
      document.body.appendChild(localStorageScript);
    }
    localStorageScript.text = 'var localStorageCache = '+JSON.stringify(_localStorageCache)+';';
    console.log('updateDOM: ', localStorageScript);
  }
}

function saveCurrentHTML() {

  exportBlob('pcjs-portable.html', ['<!doctype html>', document.documentElement.outerHTML]);

  function exportBlob(filename, textChunks) {
    try {
      var blob = new Blob(textChunks, { type: 'application/octet-stream' });
    }
    catch (blobError) {
      exportDocumentWrite(filename, textChunks.join(''));
      return;
    }
    exportBlobHTML5(filename, blob);
  }
  function exportBlobHTML5(filename, blob) {
    var url = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
    var a = document.createElement('a');
    a.href = url;
    a.setAttribute('download', filename);
    try {
      // safer save method, supposed to work with FireFox
      var evt = document.createEvent("MouseEvents");
      evt.initMouseEvent("click", true, false, window, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, false, false, false, false, 0, null);
      a.dispatchEvent(evt);
    }
    catch (e) {
      a.click();
    }
  }
  function exportDocumentWrite(filename, content) {
    var win = document.createElement('iframe');
    win.style.width = '100px';
    win.style.height = '100px';
    win.style.display = 'none';
    document.body.appendChild(win);
    setTimeout(function() {
      var doc = win.document;
      doc.open();
      doc.write(content);
      doc.close();
      doc.execCommand('SaveAs', null, filename);
    }, 200);
  } 
}

function getUniqueKey() {
  var key = window.location.pathname;

  key = key.split('?')[0];
  key = key.split('#')[0];

  key = key.toLowerCase();

  var ignoreSuffix = '/index.html';

  if (key.length > ignoreSuffix.length && key.slice(key.length - ignoreSuffix.length) === ignoreSuffix)
    key = key.slice(0, key.length - ignoreSuffix.length);

  if (key.charAt(0) === '/')
    key = key.slice(1);
  if (key.charAt(key.length - 1) === '/')
    key = key.slice(0, key.length - 1);

  if (window.location.port === 'blob:') {
    var pts = key.split('/');
    key = pts[pts.length - 1];
  }

  return key;
}
